    "The summary of search results for research articles is shown in Fig. 2.In this review, we commence with a comprehensive overview of Transformer architecture in Sect.",
    "TransformerIn this section, we begin by analyzing the inherent mechanics of the Transformer proposed by Vaswani et al. [63] in 2017, to present solutions to the challenge of neural machine translation.",
